{
    "title": "Farrapo Humano",
    "artist": "Luiz Melodia",
    "composer": "Luíz Melodia",
    "lyricsHtml": "\n[Intro] <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Eu canto, suplico, lastimo</span>\n         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Não vivo contigo</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Sou santo, sou franco</span>\n                       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Enquanto não caio não brigo</span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Me amarro, me encarno na sua</span>\n                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Mais estou pra estourar, estourar</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>                                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Eu choro tanto me escondo e não digo</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>                      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Viro farrapo tento suicídio</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Com caco de telha, com caco de vidro</span>\n\n                                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Só fala na certa repleta de felicidade</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Me calo ouvindo seu nome</span>\n            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Por entre a cidade</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Não choro, só zango, resisto</span>\n         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Eu fico no lugar, no lugar</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>                                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Eu choro tanto me escondo e não digo</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>                      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Viro farrapo tento suicídio</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Com caco de telha com caco de vidro</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Com caco de telha com caco de vidro</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Com caco de telha com caco de vidro</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>                         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Estou muito acabado tão abatido</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>                           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Minha companheira que venha comigo</span>\n                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7/9\">F7/9</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7/9\">F#7/9</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7/9\">G7/9</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7/9\">G7/9</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Mas estou  pra me    zan    gar</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7/9\">F7/9</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7/9\">F#7/9</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7/9\">G7/9</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7/9\">G7/9</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7/9\">F7/9</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7/9\">F#7/9</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7/9\">G7/9</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7/9\">G7/9</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Pra me    aca    bar,           Pra o que   que    há</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>                              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Eu choro tanto escondo e não digo</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>                       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Viro farrapo tento suicídio</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Com caco de telha com caco de vidro</span>\n                        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E da melhor maneira possível</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Com caco de telha com caco de vidro</span>\n                        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E da melhor maneira possível</span>\n",
